  "instructions": [
    "in a medium saucepan combine kombu seaweed and water and bring to a boil then reduce heat and simmer for 10 minutes",
    "remove kombu from the saucepan and discard",
    "add chicken stock concentrate ghee onion garlic carrot celery and thyme to the saucepan and cook until the vegetables are tender",
    "add xanthan gum and season with salt and black pepper",
    "strain the mixture through a fine-mesh sieve into a clean bowl and discard the solids",
    "return the mixture to the saucepan and cook until it has reduced slightly",
    "shatter the mixture by mashing it with a potato masher or whisk",
    "adjust the seasoning as needed",
    "Ensure poultry is cooked to an internal temperature of 74°C / 165°F (juices run clear, no pink remaining) before serving."
